{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-3/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"75b54429-d5c4-5127-a853-b9f982a6d2c8","excerpt":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus…","html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용</a></li>\n<li><strong>개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용</strong></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus) 적용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 5 - 블로그(GitHub Pages) 배포</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 6 - 사용자 지정 도메인 적용</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>이전 포스트에서 세팅을 완료한 <a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그</a>에 페이지네이션(pagination)을 알아보고, 적용해 보도록 할게요.</p>\n<p>블로그를 열심히 운영한다면 적게는 수십 개에서 많게는 수백, 수천 개의 포스트가 생성될 거예요.\n수많은 포스트를 불러오는 데 시간이 오래 걸릴 수 있고, 독자는 포스트를 찾는 경험이 나빠질 수 있어요.\n이런 경우 페이징 처리를 적용하면 포스트를 분할해서 시간을 단축하고, 독자는 페이지 단위로 포스트를 찾을 수가 있어요.</p>\n<p>페이징 처리는 페이지네이션(pagination), 인피니티 스크롤(infinite scroll) 방식이 있지만, 저는 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/adding-pagination/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">공식 문서를 참고하여 페이지네이션을 적용</a>하도록 할게요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/db806/pagination-preview.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pagination 적용된 결과\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/f058b/pagination-preview.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/c26ae/pagination-preview.png 158w,\n/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/6bdcf/pagination-preview.png 315w,\n/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/f058b/pagination-preview.png 630w,\n/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/40601/pagination-preview.png 945w,\n/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/78612/pagination-preview.png 1260w,\n/static/c1cf755e05e90a8d91e0740e13e2550d/db806/pagination-preview.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Pagination 적용된 결과</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>1. blog-list.js 파일 생성</h2>\n<p><strong>./src/pages/</strong> 디렉터리에 존재하는 <strong>index.js</strong> 파일을 <strong>./src/templates/</strong> 디렉터리 하위로 이동 후, <strong>blog-list.js</strong> 파일명으로 변경해 주세요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/db806/move-index-file.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.22784810126582%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1] &quot;./src/pages/index.js -&gt; ./src/templates/blog-list.js&quot; 파일 변경\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/f058b/move-index-file.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/c26ae/move-index-file.png 158w,\n/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/6bdcf/move-index-file.png 315w,\n/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/f058b/move-index-file.png 630w,\n/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/40601/move-index-file.png 945w,\n/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/78612/move-index-file.png 1260w,\n/static/eb6d4618273c5a07c06fba2e708e103f/db806/move-index-file.png 3424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1] &quot;./src/pages/index.js -&gt; ./src/templates/blog-list.js&quot; 파일 변경</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>2. gatsby-node.js 파일에서 GraphQL Query 수정 및 페이지네이션 포스트 목록 코드 추가</h2>\n<p>gatsby-node.js 파일에서 <strong>[2-1] 이미지</strong>의 1번 영역(22 ~ 30번 라인)의 GraphQL 쿼리를 2번 영역의 쿼리로 수정해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// [2-1] 이미지의 2번 영역 코드</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">allMarkdownRemark</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">sort</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">frontmatter</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">date</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">ASC</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">limit</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    edges <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      node <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        id\n        fields <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          slug\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/5abcb/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.810126582278485%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-1] GraphQL Query 수정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/f058b/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/c26ae/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 158w,\n/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/6bdcf/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 315w,\n/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/f058b/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 630w,\n/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/40601/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 945w,\n/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/78612/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 1260w,\n/static/d8b53d874a3f72c30ddfda714970ed9a/5abcb/gatsby-node-graphql-query.png 3666w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-1] GraphQL Query 수정</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>그리고 <strong>[2-2] 이미지를 참고</strong>하여 1번 코드를 2번 코드로 수정하고, 3번 코드를 4번 코드로 수정해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">// [2-2] 이미지의 2번 영역 코드</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> posts <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>allMarkdownRemark<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>edges\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// [2-2] 이미지의 4번 영역 코드</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">createPage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">path</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> post<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fields<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>slug<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">component</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> blogPost<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">context</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> post<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    previousPostId<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    nextPostId\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>5번 영역의 코드처럼 페이지네이션을 적용한 포스트 목록 코드를 추가해 주세요.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">postsPerPage</code> 변수는 포스트 목록에 보이는 포스트 개수이고, <code class=\"language-text\">numPages</code> 변수는 페이지네이션의 전체 페이지의 개수예요.<br>\n개츠비 블로그에 포스트가 현재 3개 밖에 없기 때문에 포스트 목록에서 보이는 개수는 2개로 할게요.\n그리고 현재 페이지는 URL에 path로 표현돼요. (e.g. 1페이지의 경우, 'localhost:8000/' 또는 3페이지의 경우, 'localhost:8000/3')</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> postsPerPage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> numPages <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ceil</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>posts<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> postsPerPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nArray<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">from</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">length</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> numPages <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">_<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">createPage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">path</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">/</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">component</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolve</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./src/templates/blog-list.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">context</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">limit</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> postsPerPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">skip</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> postsPerPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      numPages<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">currentPage</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/7d055/added-pagination-code.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.93670886075949%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2-2] Pagination 코드 추가\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/f058b/added-pagination-code.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/c26ae/added-pagination-code.png 158w,\n/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/6bdcf/added-pagination-code.png 315w,\n/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/f058b/added-pagination-code.png 630w,\n/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/40601/added-pagination-code.png 945w,\n/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/78612/added-pagination-code.png 1260w,\n/static/609f3de37def70020fe361b9186b92ff/7d055/added-pagination-code.png 3992w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2-2] Pagination 코드 추가</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>3. blog-list.js 파일에서 GraphQL Query 수정 및 Pagination 적용</h2>\n<p>blog-list.js 파일에서 73 ~ 94번 라인에 GraphQL을 <code class=\"language-text\">limit</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">skip</code> 추가된 쿼리로 수정해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> pageQuery <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  query blogPageQuery($skip: Int!, $limit: Int!) {\n    site {\n      siteMetadata {\n        title\n      }\n    }\n    allMarkdownRemark(\n      sort: { frontmatter: { date: DESC } }\n      limit: $limit\n      skip: $skip\n     ) {\n      nodes {\n        excerpt\n        fields {\n          slug\n        }\n        frontmatter {\n          date(formatString: \"MMMM DD, YYYY\")\n          title\n          description\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/2e788/blog-list-graphql-query.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.24050632911392%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[3-1] limit, skip 추가된 GraphQL Query\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/f058b/blog-list-graphql-query.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/c26ae/blog-list-graphql-query.png 158w,\n/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/6bdcf/blog-list-graphql-query.png 315w,\n/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/f058b/blog-list-graphql-query.png 630w,\n/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/40601/blog-list-graphql-query.png 945w,\n/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/78612/blog-list-graphql-query.png 1260w,\n/static/60687b8cbc79be1d52c14ada7422d45c/2e788/blog-list-graphql-query.png 2890w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[3-1] limit, skip 추가된 GraphQL Query</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>[3-2] 이미지를 참고하여 <code class=\"language-text\">{ data, location }</code> 코드를 <code class=\"language-text\">props</code>로 변경하고, 페이지네이션 적용에 필요한 변수를 정의해 주세요.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">currentPage</code> : 현재 페이지</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">numPages</code> : 전체 페이지 개수</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">isFirst</code> : 현재 페이지가 첫 번째 페이지 여부</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">isLast</code> : 현재 페이지가 마지막 페이지 여부</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">prevPage</code> : 이전 페이지 번호</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">nextPage</code> : 다음 페이지 번호</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> location <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>location\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> siteTitle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>site<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>siteMetadata<span class=\"token operator\">?.</span>title <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">Title</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> posts <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>allMarkdownRemark<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nodes\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> currentPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> numPages <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> props<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pageContext\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> isFirst <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentPage <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> isLast <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentPage <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> numPages\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> prevPage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentPage <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentPage <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> nextPage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentPage <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/57854/added-pagination-value.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.556962025316455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[3-2] Pagination 적용에 필요한 변수 추가\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/f058b/added-pagination-value.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/c26ae/added-pagination-value.png 158w,\n/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/6bdcf/added-pagination-value.png 315w,\n/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/f058b/added-pagination-value.png 630w,\n/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/40601/added-pagination-value.png 945w,\n/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/78612/added-pagination-value.png 1260w,\n/static/8b321f7ee826ebc6384e59f9c9dea3ab/57854/added-pagination-value.png 3368w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[3-2] Pagination 적용에 필요한 변수 추가</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>페이지네이션 구현에 필요한 모든 준비는 끝났어요. 이제 페이지네이션 적용을 위해 정의한 변수를 활용해서 페이지네이션을 구현하면 돼요.\n<code class=\"language-text\">isFrist</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">prevPage</code> 변수를 활용해서 \"← Previous Page\"가 적용되고, <code class=\"language-text\">isLast</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">nextPage</code> 변수를 활용해서 \"Next Page →\"가 적용될 거예요.\n그리고 <code class=\"language-text\">numPages</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">currentPage</code> 변수를 활용해서 페이지 번호가 보이도록 아래 코드를 참고해서 적용해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ul style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">display</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'flex'</span><span